==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Resection
<hw>Re*sec"tion</hw> <pr>(r?-s?k"sh?n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>resectio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>r⟦eacute⟧section</ets>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of cutting or paring off.</def>
<rj><au>Cotgrave.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Surg.)</fld> <def>The removal of the articular
extremity of a bone, or of the ends of the bones in a false
articulation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reseda</ent>⟦br⟧
